<item>
 <title>J. Edgar Hoover</title>
 <link>https://kennedyprize.columbia.edu/winners/2013/schenkkan/media/j-edgar-hoover</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;J. Edgar Hoover, the Director of the Federal Bureau of Investigation from 1935 - 1972, standing in the Oval Office of the White House on July 24, 1967.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
